Not Just The Same Old Fair Housing Class – 3 hrs Req Core CE
9:00 AM -
12:00 PM
35
Jeff Kester
Fair Housing: Know the Don’ts and Focus on the Do’s! Review Fair Housing Laws, Basic Concepts and Actions that can be taken to address Fair Housing issues Develop Affirmative Consideration for embedding Fair Housing as a key element in Real Estate Instructor: Jeff Kester 3 hrs 2024 Mandatory Core Requirement for MREC 2024 License Renewals Breakfast will be provided Class cancellations will be accepted until 48 hrs prior to class date. Cancellations will be refunded minus a 10% cancellation fee. No shows will be charged the full registration amount.

Web Accessibility
Web Accessibility

Greater Springfield Board of Realtors®, Inc. is committed to ensuring digital accessibility for people with disabilities. We are continually improving the user experience for everyone and applying relevant accessibility standards.

If you have difficulty accessing content, have difficulty viewing a file on the website, or notice any accessibility problems, please contact us to specify the nature of the accessibility issue and any assistive technology you use. We will strive to provide the content you need in the format you require.
